claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table showing Flublok presentation formats (single-dose prefilled syringe), carton and component NDC numbers, followed by storage and handling instructions. The image contains only product packaging identifiers and storage/handling guidelines; it does not provide any information on antigenic match with WHO- or FDA-selected strains and therefore does not support the claim.
